                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d647">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to the <persName
                            type="to">Duke de Arcos</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-09-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 18, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Referring to your personal letter 11th relative Spanish prisoners, Secretary War
                    has cabled General Otis to give every facility to Spanish commissioners for the
                    care of released prisoners.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alvey A. Adee</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
